---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About AnDong | 20+ Years of Precision CNC Machining Expertise | AnDong Co., Ltd."
  description="Founded in Taichung, Taiwan by veteran machinists, AnDong Co., Ltd. has 20+ years of precision CNC machining experience. Turn-mill, 5-axis, 3/4-axis milling, and CNC turning for diverse industries."
  active="about"
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en">Home</a> / About</div>
      <h1>About AnDong</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>AnDong Co., Ltd.</h2>
      <p>Founded by a veteran machinist with over twenty years of experience, AnDong Co., Ltd. is based in Taiping District, Taichung — Taiwan's industrial heartland. Starting with a single CNC turning machine, we have grown into a full-line precision machining shop covering turn-mill centers, 5-axis machining centers, 3/4-axis milling, and CNC turning. We serve customers across machinery, automotive, factory automation, and precision tooling industries.</p>

      <p>We believe quality is built from the details of every process step. Beyond investing in advanced machinery, we developed our own production management system integrated with networked machine monitoring (FOCAS-based). Every order — from drawing receipt, scheduling, machining, and inspection to shipment — is fully traceable, so customers always know where their parts are.</p>

      <h2>Company Milestones</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><strong>Founding</strong>: Started with CNC turning and milling, serving general mechanical parts customers</li>
        <li><strong>Expansion</strong>: Added precision 5-axis machining centers, turn-mill centers, and 4-axis milling capacity</li>
        <li><strong>Digital Transformation</strong>: Built an in-house production management system integrating drawing control, scheduling, inventory, and inspection</li>
        <li><strong>Smart Manufacturing</strong>: Deployed real-time machine monitoring with FOCAS communication and automated shift-output tracking</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Company Information</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><strong>Company Name</strong>: AnDong Co., Ltd. (銨東股份有限公司)</li>
        <li><strong>Tax ID</strong>: 83181576</li>
        <li><strong>Address</strong>: No. 22, Lane 29, Chenggong Rd., Taiping Dist., Taichung City 411, Taiwan</li>
        <li><strong>Tel</strong>: +886-4-24965670</li>
        <li><strong>Fax</strong>: +886-4-24966591</li>
        <li><strong>E-mail</strong>: andong@adcnc.com.tw</li>
        <li><strong>Business Hours</strong>: Mon-Sat 8:00-17:00 (GMT+8)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Location</h2>
      <p>Located in the Taiping industrial cluster of Taichung, with easy access from Freeway No. 3 (Zhongtou Interchange). We welcome customer visits.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 24px; aspect-ratio: 16/9; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);">
        <iframe
          src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=No.+22,+Lane+29,+Chenggong+Rd.,+Taiping+Dist.,+Taichung+City,+Taiwan&hl=en&z=17&output=embed"
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          style="border:0;"
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="AnDong Co., Ltd. Location Map"
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to work together or visit?</h2>
      <p>Reach out by phone or message — we're happy to discuss your project</p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
